data.description: Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, close to town and all the conveniences, this charming house on a HUGE lot with NO HOA is waiting for you to call it home! As you enter, the beautiful LVP floors take you past the flex space (used as an office but has endless possibilities) and into the cozy living area. The kitchen boasts granite counters and ample cabinet space, along with an eat-in area. Down the hall, you'll find 3 bedrooms and both baths. The spacious main bedroom, with plenty of closet space and room for all your furniture, has a great en-suite with tiled step in shower. The other two bedrooms are nicely sized and share the updated hall bath. Out back, you'll find a great brick/concrete patio overlooking the HUGE fenced back yard with workshop.This powered building is perfect for whatever your imagination allows! Behind it, there is another paved area to be used for another private patio, or store whatever you may need. Back in the house, you'll find the laundry room off of the kitchen, with access to a generous storage area (which could easily be finished to make more living space) and another flex space which has also been updated to include LVP flooring. This area was previously used as a second living area but, again, the possibilities are endless! This lovely home is in a perfect location; SO close to everything our area has to offer, and is priced to SELL! Get in to see it today and don't miss out!
